31:14.160 --> 31:17.080
You know about
the photograph, don't you?

31:18.800 --> 31:21.600
You don't look very
surprised or shocked.

31:23.080 --> 31:26.320
You know how the rumour mill works.

31:26.320 --> 31:31.080
People are betting on who they think
it is and who you're protecting.

31:32.360 --> 31:33.840
I'm not telling you.

31:33.840 --> 31:35.000
I'm not asking.

31:36.400 --> 31:38.240
You should know me better than that.

31:44.520 --> 31:46.160
SHE SIGHS

31:48.520 --> 31:52.520
One tiny moment,
a click of a camera.

31:55.280 --> 31:57.000
That's what's on trial, really.

31:57.000 --> 31:58.840
It's not a trial, Margaret.

31:58.840 --> 32:01.800
But I got on my knees
and enjoyed it.

32:01.800 --> 32:03.680
It is a trial.

32:05.080 --> 32:09.720
And I have to be sorry, cos the law
doesn't like women who aren't sorry.

32:09.720 --> 32:10.880
Then pretend.

32:12.160 --> 32:16.440
Ian's pretending he's a sad
and wronged noble husband.

32:16.440 --> 32:19.040
You could pretend
to be good and nice.

32:19.040 --> 32:20.880
I'll have to school
my face in remorse.

32:20.880 --> 32:22.360
Go on.

32:22.360 --> 32:23.600
Let's see it.

32:26.040 --> 32:27.920
THEY LAUGH

32:27.920 --> 32:30.280
Yes, that might need some work.Mm.

32:42.720 --> 32:44.040
Do you still love him?

32:50.080 --> 32:51.240
Does he still love you?

32:55.840 --> 32:57.120
BARTENDER CLEARS THROAT

32:58.840 --> 33:00.440
Do you think he wants us to go?

33:00.440 --> 33:01.880
THEY CHUCKLE

33:03.240 --> 33:07.000
Nightcap at mine.

33:07.000 --> 33:11.800
I'm sorry for dragging you into
all this, darling, I really am.

33:11.800 --> 33:13.440
I'm grown up.

33:13.440 --> 33:15.240
I can look after myself, remember?

33:15.240 --> 33:16.600
Mm.

33:17.680 --> 33:19.680
Thank you for being my friend.

33:19.680 --> 33:21.920
Hey, don't be soft.

33:21.920 --> 33:23.520
Always.

33:26.720 --> 33:28.080
CAMERA CLICKS

33:32.680 --> 33:34.880
Bye, darling. Bye. Love you!

33:44.320 --> 33:46.560
Public hair is fascinating.

33:46.560 --> 33:49.320
Idiosyncratic as a fingerprint.

33:49.320 --> 33:52.640
I can tell my regular
clients apart by a mere clump

33:52.640 --> 33:55.280
of the downstairs fuzz.

33:55.280 --> 33:56.960
The photograph, if you please.

34:02.920 --> 34:04.240
Mm.

34:04.240 --> 34:06.760
It's not that clear, is it?

34:04.240 --> 34:06.760
KNOCKING

34:06.760 --> 34:07.840
Come.

34:12.360 --> 34:13.760
What the fuck are you doing here?

34:13.760 --> 34:16.600
We are obliged to be present
in all matters

34:16.600 --> 34:20.280
pertaining to our client's defence.

34:20.280 --> 34:21.920
Oh, Jesus Christ.

34:26.760 --> 34:29.440
Well, then, Your Grace.

34:29.440 --> 34:31.320
Release the beast.

34:33.880 --> 34:37.120
Do you see now, you see?

34:37.120 --> 34:39.200
That's why I call her Satan.

34:40.880 --> 34:43.080
I want you to tear her to shreds.

34:45.120 --> 34:46.760
HE WINCES

34:46.760 --> 34:48.520
Apologies.

34:48.520 --> 34:50.120
A little tangle.

34:50.120 --> 34:53.000
Sir, I want to remind you that
the evidence for your case

34:53.000 --> 34:55.920
is circumstantial and flimsy at best

34:55.920 --> 34:59.360
and excessively punitive
and spiteful at worst.

34:59.360 --> 35:01.480
Your wife has endured
a lot during your marriage,

35:01.480 --> 35:03.600
and I'm confident that
the way will be far kinder

35:03.600 --> 35:04.760
to her than you've been.

35:04.760 --> 35:07.840
Well, that all depends
on the view of the judge.

35:07.840 --> 35:10.440
Your wife's in pain, Your Grace.

35:24.160 --> 35:25.640
PHONE RINGS

35:33.240 --> 35:34.720
Yes?

35:34.720 --> 35:36.920
IAN: It's me.

35:36.920 --> 35:39.520
Sorry to hear about your father.
He was a good man.

35:46.040 --> 35:49.200
I've seen you look better, Margaret.

35:49.200 --> 35:51.760
Rode hard, put away wet.

35:51.760 --> 35:53.400
That's how you look.

35:53.400 --> 35:54.680
What'd you want, Ian?

35:57.960 --> 36:01.720
I thought you and I should
have a civil conversation.

36:01.720 --> 36:05.040
As fun as all this has been,
it's gone far enough.

36:05.040 --> 36:06.800
Fun?

36:06.800 --> 36:08.160
God.

36:09.560 --> 36:12.360
Do you know I think you died
in that prisoner of war camp?

36:14.120 --> 36:15.200
You died...

36:16.800 --> 36:20.160
..and this is just a corpse
that you drag around.

36:22.600 --> 36:25.200
Because you don't feel
anything at all, do you?

36:31.520 --> 36:32.640
No.

36:36.720 --> 36:38.960
I don't know if it's the
war but you're right,

36:38.960 --> 36:42.040
I don't feel anything, really.
I never have.

36:44.160 --> 36:45.800
This...

36:47.600 --> 36:51.400
..this battle between you and I...

36:51.400 --> 36:53.240
..makes the blood bang.

36:55.880 --> 36:58.320
It's the closest I
ever got to feeling alive.

37:00.840 --> 37:01.920
Sir.

37:14.520 --> 37:16.840
You cheated my father, Ian.

37:19.360 --> 37:21.800
He trusted you, and you cheated him.

37:21.800 --> 37:26.120
He wanted you to be a Duchess.
You're a Duchess.

37:26.120 --> 37:28.560
Couldn't see anything beyond that.

37:28.560 --> 37:33.000
All you ever wanted was
his money, my money,

37:33.000 --> 37:36.840
and now you've spent it all,
and you need another rich wife.

37:36.840 --> 37:39.160
I expect you've
already got one lined up.

37:39.160 --> 37:40.880
That's what this is really about.

37:44.840 --> 37:46.200
Maybe.

37:48.040 --> 37:52.640
But for the public, this will
always be about your innumerable,

37:52.640 --> 37:54.160
flagrant infidelities.

37:56.080 --> 37:57.920
Who's the chap in the
photograph by the way?

37:57.920 --> 38:00.240
I'd like to buy him a drink
and congratulate him on the...

38:00.240 --> 38:01.680
You were never faithful to me, Ian,

38:01.680 --> 38:04.000
so let's not pretend
that's who we are.

38:04.000 --> 38:06.360
Who were my mistresses?

38:06.360 --> 38:07.480
Jane, for one.

38:10.040 --> 38:11.600
Can you prove it?

38:13.560 --> 38:19.120
Do you have love letters,
diaries, a photograph?

38:19.120 --> 38:20.600
Because I do.

38:24.160 --> 38:27.280
Here's the situation as I see it,

38:27.280 --> 38:29.360
my case can be heard by a judge,

38:29.360 --> 38:32.920
at which point details I think you
would prefer to remain private

38:32.920 --> 38:35.320
will become a
matter of legal record.

38:35.320 --> 38:36.960
Or?

38:36.960 --> 38:40.560
Pay me Â£250,000, clear my debts,

38:40.560 --> 38:42.760
pay my lawyers, and agree
to be divorced for adultery,

38:42.760 --> 38:46.200
and then all of this
unpleasantness just goes away.

38:46.200 --> 38:48.760
You want to shame
me into submission?

38:48.760 --> 38:49.880
Yes.

38:52.680 --> 38:56.160
But at least it will be all over.

38:56.160 --> 38:57.880
But it won't be over, will it, Ian?

39:00.280 --> 39:03.600
Because there'll
just be something else,

39:03.600 --> 39:06.160
then something else,

39:06.160 --> 39:10.320
and you'll hold it over me forever.

39:10.320 --> 39:13.840
I think that that's a
risk you'll have to take.

39:24.280 --> 39:26.200
Well?

39:31.240 --> 39:32.960
See you in court.

39:42.520 --> 39:44.040
CHATTER

39:54.720 --> 39:56.160
How can it be Judge Wheatley again?

39:56.160 --> 39:58.720
Let's forget Wheatley for one
second, you have bigger issues.

39:58.720 --> 40:00.600
The photograph of you
and Peter Combe...God.

40:00.600 --> 40:02.840
I should've known that
Ian would have me watched.

40:02.840 --> 40:05.040
You said there was nothing
between you and Mr Combe.

40:05.040 --> 40:07.120
And there isn't.
Peter will swear to it.

40:07.120 --> 40:09.520
How is Ian allowed
to spy on me like that?

40:09.520 --> 40:13.120
All parties in Argyll
versus Argyll. All parties.

40:13.120 --> 40:16.120
You have to drop the
counter-claim against him.

40:16.120 --> 40:18.000
We have no evidence
about your step-mother.

40:18.000 --> 40:20.320
I know that Jane and
Ian had an affair.

40:20.320 --> 40:23.320
Without evidence,
it's just speculation.

40:23.320 --> 40:27.440
You have to drop it. You have to.
Before we start.

40:47.920 --> 40:49.480
Court rise.

41:04.480 --> 41:08.120
Dr Tulloch, a material piece of
evidence against the Duchess

41:08.120 --> 41:11.680
is a polaroid photograph.
You've seen this photograph?

41:11.680 --> 41:15.680
I have. I studied it for
professional comparison.

41:15.680 --> 41:18.520
My Lord, the Defender claims
that the man in the photograph

41:18.520 --> 41:19.760
is her husband.

41:19.760 --> 41:22.240
Dr Tulloch, you examined the Duke
to establish if this was so.

41:22.240 --> 41:23.600
I did.

41:23.600 --> 41:25.280
I observed all the distributions

41:25.280 --> 41:28.000
of the suprapubic hair formation.

41:28.000 --> 41:30.560
The man in the polaroid
photograph has a thick,

41:30.560 --> 41:33.760
bushy growth that extends
towards the umbilicus.

41:33.760 --> 41:37.160
The Duke, in contrast,
has a very thin and fine

41:37.160 --> 41:38.920
suprapubic distribution.

41:38.920 --> 41:41.080
So what did you
conclude from this clearly

41:41.080 --> 41:43.800
experienced
professional examination?

41:43.800 --> 41:47.120
That the person in the photograph
was different from the Duke.

41:47.120 --> 41:48.960
Different.

41:48.960 --> 41:50.680
Not her husband.

41:53.720 --> 41:55.040
Thank you, Dr Tulloch.

41:55.040 --> 41:58.120
How would you describe your
relationship with the Defender?

42:00.360 --> 42:02.480
The Duchess and I are friends.

42:02.480 --> 42:08.280
We go for dinner, walk our dogs
together, go to the cinema.

42:08.280 --> 42:10.000
I make her laugh.

42:10.000 --> 42:14.400
She's needed that during her
marriage, someone to make her laugh.

42:14.400 --> 42:17.640
The pursuer has a photograph of you
and the Defender

42:17.640 --> 42:21.800
embracing on her doorstep in
the early hours of the morning.

42:21.800 --> 42:23.800
Yes, he does.

42:23.800 --> 42:26.720
Have you at any time
in your friendship

42:26.720 --> 42:29.760
been intimately
involved with the Defender?

42:29.760 --> 42:31.240
Never.

42:31.240 --> 42:33.840
No, we've never once
been adulterous.

42:33.840 --> 42:36.480
It's not even a remote possibility.

42:36.480 --> 42:37.880
We're friends.

42:37.880 --> 42:40.600
That embrace is the embrace that
friends give each other.

42:45.080 --> 42:48.040
INDISTINCT CHATTER

42:54.880 --> 42:57.880
My lord, I have a letter from
the Duke's physician declaring that

42:57.880 --> 43:01.840
the Duke suffers from a condition
that requires him to sit.

43:01.840 --> 43:03.040
I will allow.

43:08.920 --> 43:12.840
Yes, my wife frequently went out in
London unaccompanied by me.

43:14.720 --> 43:16.560
Sometimes she returned at midnight,

43:16.560 --> 43:19.240
sometimes at three or four o'clock
in the morning.

43:19.240 --> 43:21.360
She said she was with friends.

43:21.360 --> 43:23.720
And were you entirely happy
about that?

43:23.720 --> 43:25.400
No.

43:25.400 --> 43:26.960
All of her friends were men.

43:29.400 --> 43:31.880
She assured me it was all
completely innocent.

43:31.880 --> 43:33.360
And you believed her?

43:33.360 --> 43:35.000
Of course.

43:35.000 --> 43:38.160
But then my suspicions
became overwhelming.

43:38.160 --> 43:41.840
I moved out of our London home
into Claridge's Hotel,

43:41.840 --> 43:45.360
then after that I discovered
her letters,

43:45.360 --> 43:50.920
diaries and other things
that she kept secretly.

43:50.920 --> 43:54.040
And did you notice anything
in her diaries that took your

43:54.040 --> 43:56.960
attention particularly?

43:56.960 --> 43:59.400
A list of names and dates,

43:59.400 --> 44:00.760
names of men.

44:04.440 --> 44:06.360
And the letter V.

44:06.360 --> 44:10.080
And what does the Defender signify
with the use of the letter V?

44:13.640 --> 44:17.200
She... She signifies...

44:17.200 --> 44:19.040
..that intercourse occurred.

44:19.040 --> 44:20.760
GASPS

44:20.760 --> 44:23.280
How can you be so sure?

44:23.280 --> 44:26.960
Because it appears next
to my own name,

44:26.960 --> 44:31.000
in the early years of our marriage,

44:31.000 --> 44:32.440
when we were happy.

44:37.520 --> 44:41.080
You had intercourse with
the Defender when you were married

44:41.080 --> 44:42.920
to your previous wife.

44:42.920 --> 44:45.040
You committed adultery.

44:45.040 --> 44:48.560
I did so for the purposes
of obtaining a divorce.

44:48.560 --> 44:50.000
I see.

44:50.000 --> 44:52.880
You are practised in
calculation when it comes

44:52.880 --> 44:55.400
to obtaining a divorce.

44:55.400 --> 45:00.760
You say you left the London home
and took a suite at Claridge's,

45:00.760 --> 45:04.920
but you were reconciled with
the Defender in Paris.

45:04.920 --> 45:08.040
You shared the same room,
the same bed.

45:09.160 --> 45:11.000
Briefly.

45:11.000 --> 45:12.640
Briefly or not,

45:12.640 --> 45:16.520
at that time you condoned
what you suspected.

45:16.520 --> 45:19.000
My wife is very persuasive.

45:19.000 --> 45:21.440
There were nights at Inveraray
when I had to lock myself in

45:21.440 --> 45:23.240
the library in order
to get some sleep,

45:23.240 --> 45:25.480
and even then she would batter
on the door.

45:25.480 --> 45:26.560
LAUGHTER

45:26.560 --> 45:28.760
But you seemed prepared
to accept all that

45:28.760 --> 45:31.680
when the Defender paid for
your scheme to salvage

45:31.680 --> 45:33.840
a shipwreck from Tobermory Bay

45:33.840 --> 45:36.640
and the restoration of
Inveraray Castle.

45:36.640 --> 45:39.360
I put it to you that you only
began to care about

45:39.360 --> 45:43.240
the Defender's London lifestyle when
her money began to dry up.

45:43.240 --> 45:44.760
No, not at all.

45:44.760 --> 45:48.200
You weren't angry when the Defender
refused you money?

45:48.200 --> 45:49.240
No.

45:49.240 --> 45:50.720
You didn't physically attack her?

45:50.720 --> 45:52.600
There were no occasions of violence?

45:52.600 --> 45:53.720
No, and no.

45:53.720 --> 45:56.360
You didn't, with the help of
your daughter,

45:56.360 --> 45:59.280
terrorise the Defender by
holding her down in her bed

45:59.280 --> 46:00.840
and stealing her diary?

46:00.840 --> 46:02.280
I didn't terrorise her.

46:02.280 --> 46:07.360
I merely took her diary from her
bedside table as she reached for

46:07.360 --> 46:09.480
the telephone to call the police.

46:09.480 --> 46:11.640
My daughter Lady Jeanne will agree.

46:11.640 --> 46:13.080
I'm sure.

46:15.280 --> 46:17.600
You drink, don't you?

46:17.600 --> 46:19.440
You drink to excess.

46:27.000 --> 46:29.000
I drink the usual amount.

46:29.000 --> 46:32.000
